text: is there a way to find out how libraries are contributing to the size of my apk?

like for example, im using nispok’s snackbar library for snackbars, but im also using the android design support library for the navigation drawer. i would like to use the support library for snackbars too, but i really prefer nispok’s library due to ease of use/familiarity
but i don’t mind using the support library’s snackbar if cutting out nispok’s library will reduce the size of my apk
